text: Riksförbundet M Sverige (M Sverige), formerly Motormännens riksförbund is an organization for motor vehicle-owners in Sweden. It was established in 1922. in Malmö as "Sveriges förenade motormän". The name was changed in 1924. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1922 establishments in Sweden Category:Transport in Sweden Category:Organizations based in Sweden
